 probleme bei der nutzung von ammoniakoxidanten (1999) Acta Hydrochim Hydrobiol, 27, pp. 121-135; Sommer, S.G., Effect of composting on nutrient loss and nitrogen availability of cattle deep litter (2001) Eur J Agron, 14, pp. 123-133; Sommer, S.G., Hutchings, N.J., Ammonia emission from field applied manure and its reduction (2001) Eur J Agron, 15, pp. 1-15","Wolter, M.; I. Technol./Biosys. Eng. F. A. R. C., Bundesallee 50, 38116 Braunschweig, Germany",,,,,,,,04586859,,,,"German","Landbauforsch. Volkenrode",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-0036755359
